		label: "1 DON",
		notes: "Use the event to look for the missing pieces in the curve.",
		cards: [{ code: "EB03-060", name: "Will You Be My Servant?", img: "/Cards/EB03/EB03-060.jpg" }],
	},
	{
		label: "3 DON",
